  m_text: "How to Play\n\nJump between platforms as high as you can!\r\n\u2022 Avoid
    teachers floating in the gaps \u2014 they end your game\r\n\u2022 Spring platforms
    (green oval) bounce you higher\r\n\u2022 Orange platforms break after one jump\r\n\u2022
    Brown platforms disappear \u2014 jump fast!\r\n\u2022 Moving platforms get harder
    as you climb\r\n\u2022 Collect the rocket for a speed boost\r\n\u2022 Score =
    height \xD7 10"
